      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"reconnecting\" thing... it just feels like a lie. Like trying to fix a broken mirror that's been ground into dust. You can't piece it back together. The person in those photos had a spark, a purpose. I'm just... a heavy, hollow thing that takes up space. Everything I used to care about is just gone. It’s not even sadness anymore, it’s just nothingness.",
